         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Select <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">YES, UPS into ECO Mode</uicontrol> to
transfer to ECO Mode. The following message will appear on the display:</cmd>
            <stepxmp class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepxmp ">
